Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it for you, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why yes, it is an ice cream house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate fudge shingles...\NRocky road garage...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the middle of the night!\NWhy are you pacing like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I don't know how you\Ncan sleep at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Three AM?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awful, it's horrible, it's tragic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.\NNow do you see what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot to celebrate Arbor Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.38,0:00:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the problem is I just finished\Nplanning my schedule for the month,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but I forgot to leave time to plan\Nfor next month!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.43,0:00:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time in my schedule\Nto put together another schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I could move my meeting with\Nthe Ponyville Hay Board
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:00:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to the following Tuesday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:01:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but then I have to reschedule\Nmy lunch with Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know what a nightmare\Nshe is with scheduling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.90,0:01:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an absolute disaster.\NMy whole year could be thrown off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I woke up from\Nan ice cream dream for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 2 | Episode 20\NIt's About Time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed and Timed by GrayJeager\NGrayJeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, I think I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can find a way to read\NThe Art of Invisibility Spells,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and Farmhill's A Brief History of Canterlot\Nat the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that could leave me\Na half-hour scheduling window!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're me, but I'm me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How can there be two 'me's?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not scientifically possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not scientifically possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a very important message\Nfor you from the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from the future?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, now listen-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?\NThe future must be awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I don't have much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there some sort of epic pony war\Nin the distant future or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm from next Tuesday morning.\NBut that's not important right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Ntime travel's really possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you, I mean, I\Nfigure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The time spells are in\Nthe Canterlot archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- But that's not-\N- Really? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the\NStar Swirl the Bearded wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now, you have to listen to me.\N- Is time travel fun, or does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so many questions-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something extremely important\Nto tell you about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have a few seconds,\Nso you've got to listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, don't-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Future Twilight? Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What was she trying to warn me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Her clothes, her mane, that scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mess she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I am... or I... will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She must want me to prevent whatever\Nhorrible thing happens in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Fluttershy! The party can't start\Nuntil the party supplies get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy to... help... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I carry... the balloons next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, everypony! I've got\Nsomething really important to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no laughing matter!\NWe have a crisis on our hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just been visited\Nby myself from the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My future self tried to warn me\Nabout a horrible disaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that's gonna occur sometime\Nbefore next Tuesday morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of disaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I got sucked back into the future\Nbefore I could explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for your liiife!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever should we do, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we stop a disaster\Nif we don't know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to work together\Nto make sure we're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, you and the other pegasi\Nspread out over Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and look for any kind of problem\Nthat could lead to a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony else...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anypony else wanna panic with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony else,\Ntime to disaster proof Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Done, and done, and done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack,\Nwhat about the Everfree Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The perimeter's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And my team gave the all clear\Nfrom Fillydelphia to Las Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've done everything on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Future Twilight looked like\Nshe'd been through a horrible ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have this nagging feeling\Nwe should be looking for something bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,than loose bolts and leaky pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everypony.\NFollow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is that thing?\N- That's Cerberus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's supposed to be guarding\Nthe gates of Tartarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he's here, then all the ancient evil\Ncreatures that have been imprisoned there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,could escape and destroy Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Destroy Equestria?!\N- Yeah, isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Cerberus! You look like\Nyou could use some obedience training!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic obedience training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the cute widdle three-headed dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I knew you were good with animals,\Nbut this is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, he's just a big furry guy\Nwho got out of his yard, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Cerberus?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's a good boy? Who's a good boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pinkie.\N- Yes, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a ball I can borrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have balls stashed all over Ponyville.\NIn case of ball emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Cerberus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back as soon as I've returned him\Nto the gates of Tartarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he's back at home,\Nthere'll be no disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish Twilight would go on\Nepic adventures more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Best night's sleep I've had in weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Twilight.\NHow'd it go with Cerberus?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! I got him back before any\Nof the evil creatures could escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal,\Nit's just a 'lost dog' flyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the Princess hasn't heard\Nwe found Cerberus yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that,\Nit's this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A paper cut...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight,\Nyou really need to toughen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just clean it out and you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The cut's in the exact same spot\Nas the scar on future Twilight's cheek!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't changed the future at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The disaster is still coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If the disaster wasn't caused\Nby Cerberus getting loose,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,then what could it possibly be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno, but maybe you ought\Nto give the pacing a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've worn a groove into the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for another one\Nof your lectures, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My lectures?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I did everything I could think of\Nto change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe it's not what I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's what I don't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stand right here and don't\Nmove a muscle until next Tuesday,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly do whatever it is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that future Twilight wanted\Nto warn me not to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So... no matter what happens,\Nyou're not gonna move a muscle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe you won't mind if I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,eat an entire tub of ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, stop!\NThink of the stomach ache!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stomach ache, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's future Spike's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Another pegasus just got back\Nfrom Baltimare with an all-clear and-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NAren't you gonna stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, she's not gonna move\N'til next Tuesday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks it'll prevent\Nthe disaster from happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is too rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Twilight!\NThere's a mouse right behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, let me try!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! I didn't mean to!\NIt was a total accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure that's a-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! This is the same\Nmane cut as future Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know...\NIt really doesn't look too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how it looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just another sign\Nthat the future hasn't changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not doing anything didn't work either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish there was a way to know what\Nwas going to happen so I could stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna see the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I might know somepony who can help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Madame Pinkie's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Pinkie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come... enter the chamber\Nof Madame Pinkie Pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For the answers you seek, let us consult\Nthe mystical orb of fate's destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like\Nmy mystical orb of fate's destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got it. Cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh... best one I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look deep into the crystal ball...\NFor soon it will reveal all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah yes, I see something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a vision of the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You will get...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:12:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a really cool birthday present next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Cool birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, I need your Pinkie Sense\Nto tell me what the impending
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,disaster is that future Twilight\Nwas trying to warn me about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my fortune telling has nothing to do\Nwith my Pinkie Sense, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only good for vague\Nand immediate events.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that even come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I haven't seen Twilight\Nsince the flowerpot incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope she still isn't mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Off by point zero two from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry the fifteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative azimuth on the fourteenth moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight's really serious about finding out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,about that cool birthday present, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?\NAs long as I can keep eating ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, future Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Pinkie, I'm glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help me recalibrate the apertures
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,on the nine and quarter\Ncatadioptric telescopes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After I came to see Madame Pinkie\Nand the flowerpot landed on my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,see the bandage, just like\Nthe bandage from the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an epiphany after that flowerpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing things didn't work,\Nnot doing things didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't predict the future either,\Nso I only had one other choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Monitor everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That way no matter what happens\Nin the future, I'll be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I saw something last night\Nin the Horsehead nebula.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But after staring at it\Nfor three straight hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hours? But when did you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I didn't sleep. I haven't slept\Nsince future Twilight was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only three days\Nleft until next Tuesday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sleep all I want after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been awake too long, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Tuesday's not three days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuesday's tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, did you finish\Nrecalibrating the apertures
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,on the nine and quarter inch\Ncatadioptric telescopes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Twilight,\NI have eye patches stashed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,all over Ponyville,\Nin case of eye patch emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Now you look like a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A sleepy pirate,\Nwith a really weird mane cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The eye patch...! Another sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nearly all the signs have come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't done a thing\Nto prevent the catastrophe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If Tuesday's tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and the disaster happens\Nby Tuesday morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's only one solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,stop time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, the Canterlot archives\Nare right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we need\Nto sneak around, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not illegal\Nto walk around Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno why we have\Nto wear these things, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we wearing them for fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's nothing fun about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you sure?\N- Focus, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to prevent this disaster\Nis to stop time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Time spells are kept in\Nthe Star Swirl the Bearded wing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the most secure section of the archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're sneaking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!\NThat sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't understand\Nhow sneaking into the archives
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is gonna help her find out\Nabout her birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The coast is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now slowly lift me into the window\Nso we can- AH!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, if my calculations are correct,\Nthe Star Swirl the Bearded wing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,should be right... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this where we came in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! Can we climb in the window again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.\NIt's supposed to be right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to find it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should ask somepony\Nin the Star Swirl the Bearded wing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. How'd I miss that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all those\Npriceless magic scrolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more than I ever imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, the guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, what do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Twilight,\Nhaven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me open that for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I look just like future Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The last sign has come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's bad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost Tuesday morning!\NThe disaster could happen at any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do we find\Nthe time-stopping spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a million scrolls here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I. Don't. Know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:18:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, it's over!\NIt's officially Tuesday morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuesday morning, the disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno, Twilight.\NI don't see any disasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a pretty nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Twilight,\Nlove the new hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, happy Tuesday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't anypony surprised\Nto see me sneaking around in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible\Nthere never was a disaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That I've just been making myself\Nfrantic over nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If future Twilight wasn't\Nwarning you about a disaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,then what was she trying to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. But I do know one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I look ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all because\NI couldn't stop worrying
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and let the future handle itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I'm gonna\Nsolve problems as they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And stop worrying about\Nevery little thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean there won't be\Nany more late night pacing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No more late night pacing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had learned\Nthis lesson a week ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we wouldn't have had\Nto go through all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, Twilight, I found something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't stop time,\Nbut it lets you go back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It says you can go back once,\Nand it only lasts for a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that help?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, you're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can go back and tell past Twilight\Nthat she doesn't need to go berserk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with worry about a disaster\Nthat's never gonna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're me, but I'm me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How can there be two 'me's?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not scientifically possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not scientifically possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a very important message\Nfor you from the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from the future?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, now listen-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?\NThe future must be awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I don't have much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there some sort of epic pony war\Nin the distant future or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm from next Tuesday morning.\NBut that's not important right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Ntime travel's really possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you, I mean, I figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The time spells are in\Nthe Canterlot archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- But that's not-\N- Really? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the\NStar Swirl the Bearded wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now, you have to listen to me.\N- Is time travel fun, or does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so many questions-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something extremely important\Nto tell you about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have a few seconds,\Nso you've got to listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,waste your time... worrying... about...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I just did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you tell her about\Nthe cool birthday present?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember last week when future Twilight\Ncame to warn me about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That was me trying to warn myself\Nnot to worry so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm gonna spend the next week\Nfreaking out about a disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't even exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:21:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\NIt's past Twilight's problem now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, I guess you're right, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... my stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's all that ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the stomach ache\Nwould be future Spike's problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I am future Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, future Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get you home.
